<p>Sub: <strong>Verification of subject-wise roll list - Reg.</strong></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p style=3D"text-align: justify;">As per the Senate approved Academic Calen=
dar for Jan-May 2016 semester, the last date for dropping of courses<strong=
>
</strong>is over on 15<sup>th</sup> March 2016 (Tuesday). </p>
<p style=3D"text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style=3D"text-align: justify;">Hence, all the students / scholars are in=
formed that if they attend any courses without their name appearing in that=
 subject-wise roll list that course will be treated as &#8220;<strong>audit=
ing only&#8221;</strong> and grades will not be
 updated. Similarly, if you are not attending classes for any course where =
your name is appearing in the subject-wise roll list then attendance &#8220=
;Poor&#8221; and grade &#8220;W&#8221; will be given for the same.</p>
